nhc_headline: ...HEAVY RAINS AND GUSTY WINDS POSSIBLE OVER PORTIONS OF BAJA CALIFORNIA SUR ON TUESDAY AND WEDNESDAY...
summary: ...HEAVY RAINS AND GUSTY WINDS POSSIBLE OVER PORTIONS OF BAJA CALIFORNIA SUR ON TUESDAY AND WEDNESDAY... As of 5:00 PM MST Mon Oct 06 the center of Priscilla was located near 18.8, -108.0 with movement NNW at 8 mph. The minimum central pressure was 972 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 85 mph.
